#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "*‘Save the World or Aviation’. Photo: XR Sverige.*\n"
msgstr "*\"Sauver le monde ou l'aviation\". Photo : XR Suède.*\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:135
msgid ""
"A SAS domestic flight was delayed for an hour at Ängelholm–Helsingborg "
"Airport, when a brave [XRSweden](https://twitter.com/ExtinctionR_SV) rebel "
"‘superhero’ "
"[glued](https://www.facebook.com/extinctionrebellionsverige/videos/988024691658664/) "
"**herself to the plane.**"
msgstr ""
"Un vol intérieur de la compagnie SAS a été retardé d'une heure à l'aéroport d"
"'Ängelholm-Helsingborg, une courageuse rebelle d'[XRSweden](https://twitter."
"com/ExtinctionR_SV) s'étant [supergluée](https://www.facebook.com/"
"extinctionrebellionsverige/videos/988024691658664/) **à l'avant de l'avion.**"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:137
msgid ""
"On the day Swedish airports reopened, rebels protested government bailouts "
"of the aviation industry as part of its Covid-19 recovery."
msgstr ""
"Le jour de la réouverture des aéroports suédois, les rebelles ont dénoncé le "
"plan de relance du gouvernement pour renflouer de l'industrie aéronautique "
"suite à la pandémie de Covid-19."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:139
msgid ""
"The rebels called on Sweden to stop funding polluters and use public money "
"to invest in green jobs and design a sustainable economy. They said: “Our "
"action was not directed at airline workers or individual passengers. **This "
"is about the need to change the whole system.”**"
msgstr ""
"Les rebelles ont appelé la Suède à cesser de financer les grands pollueurs, "
"à investir l'argent public dans des emplois verts, et à envisager une "
"économie durable. Ils ont déclaré : \"Notre action ne visait pas les "
"travailleurs des compagnies aériennes ni les passagers individuels. **Elle "
"fait écho à la nécessité de changer tout le système\".**"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:141
msgid ""
"The non-violent protest was part of Extinction Rebellion Europe’s Bail Out "
"The Planet action wave. 5 rebels were briefly detained by the police."
msgstr ""
"Cette action directe non violente s'inscrivait dans le cadre de la vague "
"d'actions \"Bail Out The Planet\" d'XR Europe. 5 rebelles ont été brièvement "
"détenus par la police."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:143
msgid "![Photograph of victorious Swedish rebels.](/assets/uploads/19.jpg)"
msgstr "![Photograph of victorious Swedish rebels.](/assets/uploads/19.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:145
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Photo: XR Sverige.*\n"
msgstr "*Photo : XR Suède.*\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:147
msgid ""
"In a second action on 29 June rebels delayed a SAS flight from Gothenburg to "
"Stockholm by [refusing to sit "
"down.](https://www.facebook.com/extinctionrebellionsverige/videos/3010068952552974/)"
msgstr ""
"Le 29 juin, lors d'une seconde action, les rebelles ont retardé un vol SAS "
"de Göteborg à Stockholm [en refusant de s'asseoir avant le "
"décollage.](https://www.facebook.com/extinctionrebellionsverige/videos/"
"3010068952552974/)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:149
msgid ""
"Rebels stated ‘These subsidies mean that Sweden cannot live up to the Paris "
"Agreement and its own climate goals (...) Just as I would break a car window "
"on a hot day to save a child or a dog, I sound an alarm because we are in a "
"planetary emergency.’"
msgstr ""
"Des rebelles ont déclaré : \"Ces financements signifient que la Suède ne "
"peut pas respecter l'accord de Paris, et tenir ses propres objectifs "
"climatiques (...) Tout comme je briserais la vitre d'une voiture par une "
"chaude journée pour sauver un enfant ou un chien, je tire la sonnette "
"d'alarme parce que nous sommes dans une situation d'urgence planétaire.’"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:151
msgid "The rebels now face fines and **up to 6 months in jail.**"
msgstr ""
"Les rebelles encourent maintenant des amendes, et **jusqu'à 6 mois de "
"prison.**"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*Once again we have too many actions for one newsletter. To catch up on all "
"the actions that have been happening around the world - and especially "
"during Europe's week-long wave of actions - you’ll have to [read XR "
"Unchained.](https://rebellion.global/blog/2020/07/16/xr-unchained-16/) It’s "
"choc full of beauty, courage, and inspiration.*\n"
msgstr ""
